  "texts": [
    "Different from original InfoNCE loss [117], MI-InfoNCE loss enlarges the quantity of positive samples in each minibatch, which is more appropriate for the current situation.",
    "After pretraining on large video dataset, the video feature x * i from the last layer of V-Network will serve as the static context feature f s ∈ R C in our model.",
    "D. Collaborative Video Generating BranchAfter achieving the dynamic motion feature f d and tatic context feature f s, we further conduct a collaborative video generating branch based on TGAN v2 [77] to learn more comprehensive video features by fusing these two features.",
    "This branch consists of three main components: a feature integration layer, a video reconstruction network and a video prediction network.",
    "Feature Integration Layer."
